summary: This mod allows you to travel to the moon or planets you will hop in a spaceship and you are able to fly to planets check me out for more info...
descriptionHtml:
I will not be working on this mod any more D:

This mod allows you to travel to the moon or planets you will hop in a spaceship and you are able to fly to planets and fight what's out there and meet with the crew at the space port on the moon note the drop pod do not have any place to go yet I can not think of any more planets.

To get to different worlds go to the top level of the spaceship and click on the counter in front of the seat it will take you to space then go back to the counter and click on a well that you want to travel to and you will travel there

Travel places
forerunner end part [still in making]
The moon
Mars
Slender man game
falmer planet
aradox
and lots more

you can like me at [shyrim mods for pc] on facebook
